                    <h2>PRODUCT EXCHANGE, RETURN & MONEY REFUND POLICY OF LIFEONE</h2>
                    <p>We at LIFE ONE WILLNESS INDUSTRIES PRIVATE LIMITED offer a 100% Satisfaction Guarantee on our products. This indicates that consumers of Life One Willness products will be satisfied with their purchases. In any case, if the customer/direct seller is not satisfied with the product quality or any manufacturing or packaging defect is found in the product then the customer/direct seller can return/exchange the product. The Product Return Policy is applicable on saleable product(s) as well as partially used product(s). The customer/direct seller must contact the company (LIFE ONE WILLNESS INDUSTRIES PRIVATE LIMITED) from whom he/she purchased the same. Product return/exchange is subjected to the following reasons:</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>The customer/direct seller should have a valid reason for product return/exchange. </li>
                        <li>The customer/direct seller may return/exchange the product(s) within 30 days from the date of purchase. After 30 days, product return/exchange is not possible.</li>
                        <li>The product(s) exchange/return is only possible once within 30 days from the date of purchase.</li>
                        <li>The customer/direct seller must have the original copy of the purchase invoice which he/she needs to deposit with the company along with duly filled and signed Product Return Form and product(s). A Softcopy of the Product Return Form is available in the download section of the company’s website <a href="http://lifeonewellness.com/">lifeonewellness.com</a></li>
                        <li>In case of manufacturing or packaging defect in the product, the company will exchange the product(s) free of cost but the product(s) should be unopened, and unaltered.</li>
                        <li>In case of customer/direct seller wants to exchange the product(s) with another product(s), the company will issue a credit note (Zero BV) of the same amount, which can be used by the customer/direct seller within 30 days of his/her first purchase for purchasing other products of his/her choice. Product(s) exchange is only possible if the product(s) are unopened (sealed), physically undamaged, and should be useable, resaleable, and unaltered.</li>
                        <li>
                            If the customer/direct seller wants his/her money back due to any reason, the Company shall initiate the money-back process and shall provide a full refund for the product(s) to the customer/direct seller after deducting GST amount. Money back is possible only if:<br>

                            <ol>
                                <li>Product(s) seal is open and customer/direct seller has used the product: used quantity of the product(s) should not be used more than 25% of the total product quantity. For example, if a product contains 60 capsules at the time of purchase, then at the time of return, the balance product quantity must not be less than 45 capsules.</li>
                                <li>Product(s) are sealed: product(s) should not be physically damaged, and should be useable, resaleable, and unaltered.</li>
                                <li>The company shall use the same mode to return the amount in lieu of the product(s) returned. It means, if the customer/direct seller has used the online transaction at the time of product(s) purchase, the company shall online transfer the amount to the same bank account of customer/direct seller.</li>
                                <li>If the amount of refund in lieu of product(s) returned is up to Rs.1000/-, the company shall immediately return back cash amount to the customer/direct seller. However, if the amount will exceed Rs.1000/-, then the company shall transfer the said amount to the customer's/direct seller's bank account.</li>

                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>Product Return Policy is NOT APPLICABLE on Business Support Materials (BSM), Brochures, Product Literatures, Electric items if opened.</li>
                        <li>If products return quantity is greater than or equal to 6 on a single invoice, 10% handling charges will be deducted.</li>
                        <li>Total product return quantity cannot exceed the quantity appearing on the purchase invoice.</li>

                    </ol>
